{"meta":{"authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}],"title":"","dates":{"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:14:03 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:14:03 UTC"}},"nodes":[{"index":0,"parent_index":-1,"body":"<p class=\"Paragraph\">The future is formed by placing after the verb the particles: <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་རེད་</span> (assertive) or <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡིན་</span> (intentional egophoric). These are composed by adding the essential copula <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རེད་</span> or <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཡིན་</span> to the suffix<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"> གི་</span>. In written Tibetan,<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"> གི་</span> has several possible variants according to the final consonant of the preceding syllable. The pattern of these variants is the same as in the case of the genitive, except for vowels and the letter<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"> འ་</span>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་</span> is used after vowels and <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">འ་</span>, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ག་</span>,<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"> ང་&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཀྱི་ </span>is used after <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ད་</span>, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བ་</span>, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ས་</span>, and the second crypted suffix <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ད་&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; </li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གྱི་</span> is used after <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ན་</span>, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མ་</span>, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ར་</span>, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལ་&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">In Spoken Tibetan, the suffix is pronounced gi in all cases.</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">The intentional form <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡིན་</span> may be used only with volitional verbs in the first person. In interrogative sentences, the egophoric form <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡིན་ </span>is replaced by<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"> གས་ </span>if the statement contains no interrogative pronoun, and by <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ག་</span> otherwise.</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">The different forms are given in the following table:</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><strong>Table: The Future Auxiliaries</strong></p>\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Affirmative</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"136\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Interrogative</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">(without pronoun)</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Interrogative</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">(with pronoun)</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Negative</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Negative Interrogative</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡིན་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"136\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡིན་པས་</span></p>\n<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">གས་</p>\n</span></td>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ག་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་མིན་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་མིན་པས་</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་རེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"136\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་རེད་པས་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་རེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་མ་རེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"113\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་མ་རེད་པས་</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Some basic example sentences:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སང་ཉིན་མོག་མོག་བཟོ་གི་ཡིན།</span> &ldquo;Tomorrow I shall make momos.&rdquo;</li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སང་ཉིན་མོག་མོག་བཟོ་གི་རེད།</span> &ldquo;Tomorrow he/she will make momos.&rdquo;</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Affirmative</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Interrogative</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">(without pronoun)</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Interrogative</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">(with pronoun)</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Negative</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Negative Interrogative</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡིན་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡིན་པས་</span></p>\n<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">གས་</p>\n</span>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">གས་</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ག་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་མིན་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་མིན་པས་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་རེད་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་རེད་པས་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་རེད་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་མ་རེད་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་མ་རེད་པས་</span></p>\n","title":""}]}